    description:
      '**Remote | Flexible Hours | High Growth Tech Company | Fast-paced Team\u00c2\u00a0| Modern Technologies & Codebase | Leadership Opportunities**\n\n**About\u00c2\u00a0us**\u00c2\u00a0\n\nAffinda\u00c2\u00a0is a rapidly growing artificial intelligence company\u00c2\u00a0HQ\u00e2\u0080\u0099d\u00c2\u00a0in Melbourne, with a global presence. Our mission is simple \u00e2\u0080\u0093 make AI that is\u00c2\u00a0better than humans\u00c2\u00a0at extracting insights and data from documents.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nWe are a world class team of software developers, data\u00c2\u00a0scientists\u00c2\u00a0and\u00c2\u00a0AI engineers.\u00c2\u00a0We build sophisticated AI solutions that leverage the latest advancements in natural language processing and image recognition. We\u00e2\u0080\u0099ve built out the infrastructure to rapidly develop customised AI solutions designed to read,\u00c2\u00a0understand\u00c2\u00a0and process unstructured data.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nOur solutions are trusted by over 500 companies\u00c2\u00a0across the world, included\u00c2\u00a0in\u00c2\u00a0the\u00c2\u00a0ASX\u00c2\u00a0100\u00c2\u00a0and Fortune 500.\u00c2\u00a0\n\n**About the role**\u00c2\u00a0\n\nOne of our products is Draftable, a simple yet sophisticated solution\u00c2\u00a0that\u00c2\u00a0makes\u00c2\u00a0it easy\u00c2\u00a0for anyone\u00c2\u00a0to review changes\u00c2\u00a0to\u00c2\u00a0business\u00c2\u00a0documents.\u00c2\u00a0Our users compare\u00c2\u00a0millions of documents each year across our\u00c2\u00a0web service, desktop software and developer API.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nYou will be the technical lead for\u00c2\u00a0the\u00c2\u00a0front-end\u00c2\u00a0of our\u00c2\u00a0Draftable\u00c2\u00a0product\u00c2\u00a0suite,\u00c2\u00a0including\u00c2\u00a0our intuitive comparison viewer\u00c2\u00a0sitting at\u00c2\u00a0the\u00c2\u00a0centre of each\u00c2\u00a0user\u00e2\u0080\u0099s\u00c2\u00a0experience.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nYou will be working with our Product Lead and other team members to prioritise and build features.\u00c2\u00a0You will spend at least\u00c2\u00a080% of your time thinking about how to implement things and writing code.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nWe are growing rapidly, so there are plenty of opportunities for career growth.\u00c2\u00a0We expect you to take an active role in evolving our engineering culture.\u00c2\u00a0Over time, we expect you to be a pivotal\u00c2\u00a0member\u00c2\u00a0in leading\u00c2\u00a0front-end\u00c2\u00a0projects\u00c2\u00a0across\u00c2\u00a0Affinda.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nThis role can potentially be done at two levels: Lead software engineer or\u00c2\u00a0Staff software engineer.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nThis role can be performed\u00c2\u00a0fully\u00c2\u00a0remotely,\u00c2\u00a0or if\u00c2\u00a0you are based in Melbourne, you are welcome at our new office across from Fed Square.\u00c2\u00a0\n\n**About you**\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You are\u00c2\u00a0either\u00c2\u00a0an expert front-end developer\u00c2\u00a0or an experienced full-stack developer.\u00c2\u00a0(We are all about adding great people to the team, rather than finding someone who fits perfectly into a fixed slot.)\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You have 5+ years of experience with front-end development\u00c2\u00a0(Typescript,\u00c2\u00a0JS/ES6,\u00c2\u00a0CSS, HTML)\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You\u00c2\u00a0have\u00c2\u00a02+\u00c2\u00a0years\u00c2\u00a0of experience with\u00c2\u00a0React\u00c2\u00a0or a similar\u00c2\u00a0framework\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You are a great communicator. You appreciate the importance of clear communication, especially when working\u00c2\u00a0with\u00c2\u00a0a remote team.\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You\u00c2\u00a0are independent and self-reliant. You\u00c2\u00a0are happy working on a task by yourself,\u00c2\u00a0but you will take initiative to involve other team members when\u00c2\u00a0necessary\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You have a\u00c2\u00a0high attention to detail.\u00c2\u00a0You\u00c2\u00a0are intimately\u00c2\u00a0familiar\u00c2\u00a0with\u00c2\u00a0the complexities\u00c2\u00a0of\u00c2\u00a0web development,\u00c2\u00a0e.g.\u00c2\u00a0mobile\u00c2\u00a0responsiveness,\u00c2\u00a0browser\u00c2\u00a0compatibility\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You have a\u00c2\u00a0great sense of design.\u00c2\u00a0You like\u00c2\u00a0building\u00c2\u00a0software that delights users.\u00c2\u00a0\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You have experience being the technical lead of a project and are comfortable both planning/architecting as well as diving into code as an individual contributor.\u00c2\u00a0\n\n* You are fluent in English, both written and spoken, and can participate in an English-only work environment\n\n**About our culture**\u00c2\u00a0\n\nWe are a small, friendly team of experienced professionals, and trust is at the core of our culture. We are all great at what we do and appreciate the value of working with highly competent peers.\u00c2\u00a0Collaboration is key to our success, and our flat structure ensures that we reach decisions quickly. We love to get things done.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nOur development process is product-led.\u00c2\u00a0We are agile (but not Agile).\u00c2\u00a0We like short milestones. We launch things as soon as they\u00e2\u0080\u0099re ready. We like iterating based off user feedback. We do things right the first time, even if it takes a little longer. We don\u00e2\u0080\u0099t have much technical debt. We like good documentation.\u00c2\u00a0From\u00c2\u00a0time to\u00c2\u00a0time\u00c2\u00a0we promise a feature to customer, but we otherwise don\u00e2\u0080\u0099t have many external deadlines.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nWe understand you have a life outside\u00c2\u00a0work\u00c2\u00a0and we will respect your non-working and family\u00c2\u00a0time.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nOur core collaboration hours are 12pm-8pm AEST (GMT+10). You will need to have at least 3 hours overlap.\n\nOur\u00c2\u00a0services are very stable, and we haven\u00e2\u0080\u0099t had any critical incidents over the last year that required urgent attention from someone in this role.\u00c2\u00a0\n\nAffinda is an equal opportunity employer and is committed to building a team that represents a diversity of backgrounds, perspectives,\u00c2\u00a0skills\u00c2\u00a0and experiences.\u00c2\u00a0\u00c2\u00a0\n',
